  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Boutique Chain showcase emphasizing Submersion Engine as primary effect. OBLONG with wide-open filter (high cutoff, low res) provides clean harmonic material. Submersion at 8 stages — maximum all-pass cascade — and LFODepth 0.72 creates a deeply phasing spatial texture where the all-pass phase rotation is audible as a slow, lush movement through the stereo field. LFORate 0.18 Hz. LoopFB 0.42 builds a feedback loop that sustains the phasing texture even after notes end. Anomaly TextureBlend 0.35 for minimal texture layer. Cathedral SunMix 0.8 (bright cathedral character to match the open OBLONG filter). A luminous, weightless aether texture defined entirely by the all-pass rotation.",
